Maxchars (GUI item property)
============================

The maximum number of chars that this item will allow.

This property is restricted to the [editDef](EditDef\_(GUI\_item\_type)) item type.

Syntax
------

`maxchars `*`chars`*

Default value
-------------

`128`

Example(s)
----------

`maxchars 40`


